{"tid":1432590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"示威要小心！北京「監測員 」網上貼相舉報：抽出亂港分子","createTime":"2019-08-08T09:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T09:46:47.000Z","uid":71237,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"879e9b0e026427f89235c104d24010971d20ee14","tid":1432590,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:20:27.000Z","msg":"香港爆發反送中逆權運動近兩個月，北京當局近日開始進行輿論導向，招募「輿情監測員 」挖掘、蒐集、整理抹黑國家形象的幕後黑手。網上更散播「國家安全機關舉報受理平台」的訊息，呼籲將「暴徒」的照片及資料提供給國家，「只要憑照片與回鄉證做校對，就可以抽出搞亂我們香港的垃圾分子！為國家盡一分力！踢走反共勢力！」據報，對防範、制止間諜行為或偵破間諜案件提供特別線索者，最高可獲50萬元人民幣（約55萬港元）的獎勵。不過，有網民踢爆只為阻嚇港人，該網站所有舉報皆不會公開。<br />\n<br />\n「國家安全機關舉報受理平台」（ <a href=\"https://www.12339.gov.cn/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.12339.gov.cn%2F&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO74MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=1870ac76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.12339.gov.cn/</a> ）自2018年4月15日起接受組織和個人的匿名舉報，任何組織和個人可通過登錄該網站，對發現的危害國家安全犯罪行為、間諜行為，以及其他危害國家安全行為的情況線索進行舉報，也可以撥打舉報電話「12339」，國家安全機關將對舉報屬實、為維護國家安全作出積極貢獻的，國家安全機關將予以獎勵；如借舉報名義故意捏造、謊報情況或誣告他人的，妨礙國家安全機關工作或造成其他不良社會影響的，國家安全機關將依法追究其法律責任。<br />\n德國墨卡托中國研究中心訪問學人、中國國家安全問題專家霍夫曼（Samantha Hoffman）說：「宣傳運動的中心是『人人有責』參與中國的國家安全。參與的目的是防止、制止和懲罰那些可能損害國家安全的行為。」<br />\n<br />\n去年年底，中國更新了《反間諜法》，對有損國家安全、需加以懲罰的行為擴大了定義。若境外個人或團體捏造、歪曲事實或發布有損中國國家安全的訊息，政府可以對其進行處罰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190808/large/1565231176_9efa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190808%2Flarge%2F1565231176_9efa.jpg&h=193a19e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190808/59909648\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190808%2F59909648&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO74MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=956e00ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190808%2F59909648&h=6bb97f85\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190808/59909648</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc105f3d45d84fb66ae8573369132f6239449275","tid":1432590,"uid":76922,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:24:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1df06gr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1df06gr.png&h=8c2fa3c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u0QkmPM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu0QkmPM.png&h=716e9254&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yvQDSWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyvQDSWs.png&h=d18ba813&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0kE9e9N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0kE9e9N.jpg&h=65fe498a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7f2ZCn8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7f2ZCn8.jpg&h=e0b4dc49&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FOZdGPO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFOZdGPO.jpg&h=bef09638&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3226d4da6051a80a0f92c3404bd40c65e1dc00d9","tid":1432590,"uid":298077,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:26:17.000Z","msg":"我地1000暴徒,一人50萬人仔,即500000000<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n共共夠錢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d851edaa4c1da3838de670b6f4c3b4efe7c547","tid":1432590,"uid":33473,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:27:18.000Z","msg":"以後唔會上去<br />\n除非中共倒台我再考慮"},{"pid":"6b0ea